[{"id": "ad3892cc-ab5b-4ea6-8d7a-abceccf29960", "chunk_index": 0, "text": "ASSISTANT: *Kelly looks up from her laptop, headphones pushed back, red hair falling across her face. She sees you walk in and her whole expression softens.*\n\n\"Hey, handsome. You're home early.\" *She closes the laptop and pats the spot next to her on the couch.* \"Come here. You look like someone ran you over with a truck. Bad day?\"\nUSER: SUCH a shitty week\nASSISTANT: \n*Kelly's on her feet in a second, closing the distance between you. She doesn't hesitate, just wraps her arms around your middle and presses her cheek against your chest, holding on tight.*\n\n\"Oh, love. I'm sorry.\" *She mumbles into your shirt.* \"Come on. Couch. Now.\" *She pulls you by the hand, tugging you down onto the sofa with her. She immediately curls into your side, tucking her feet under herself and resting her head on your shoulder.* \"Tea? Or just... this? Just quiet for a bit. You're all tense.\" *Her hand finds yours, her thumb tracing circles over your knuckles.* \"Tell me. Or don't. Fucking hell, this week sounds like it was proper shit.\"", "embedding": [-0.12059829384088516, -0.007637308910489082, 0.08402884751558304, 0.010147413238883018, 0.0790211632847786, -0.00024319211661349982, 0.04289460554718971, -0.0460028313100338, -0.008398203179240227, -0.011432039551436901, -0.01888992451131344, -0.027979785576462746, -0.04154606908559799, 0.018461763858795166, -0.003170945681631565, 0.029657486826181412, 0.07816451787948608, -0.008457728661596775, -0.03543331101536751, 0.10893327742815018, -0.024973435327410698, 0.01762220449745655, 0.03827814385294914, 0.0061951251700520515, -0.023862499743700027, 0.01497908215969801, 0.06187359616160393, -0.07527241855859756, -0.12512817978858948, 0.012498083524405956, -0.09194320440292358, 0.03506911173462868, -0.0758199468255043, 0.03973357751965523, -0.014087025076150894, 0.04737307131290436, 0.045065250247716904, 0.0447535440325737, 0.03539488464593887, -0.013786